[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    167[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The two HIGH findings (PHI retention on DynamoDB, SQS queue handling) are both genuine gaps that a production deployment would need to address for HIPAA compliance. Neither is "you'll get breached tomorrow" critical, but both represent design decisions about PHI lifecycle that the recipe should guide the reader on.
